Hello, GPU<pre><code>export fn main {
  // Create a buffer of memory on the GPU
  let b = GBuffer([1, 2, 3, 4]);
  // Map the values into a new buffer on the GPU
  let out = b.map(fn (val: gi32) = val + 2);
  // Read the results back to RAM and print them
  out.read{i32}.print;
}
</code></pre> <p>Get Started with Alan</p> Looking for Alan v0.1? <p>Documentation for Alan v0.1 can be found on the legacy documentation website.</p>
